        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1269667209" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5907686816292030701">I enjoyed this slice of late 1700s London life. This follows a few young adults through a year in London. We get a taste of the times, no major drama, just a good feel for life in that year. The catalyst for the book seems to be the poet William Blake whom we meet as well through his friendship with these kids. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


